From Christopher Mussack Subject Re Sin In article A Jill Anne Daley writes What exactly is a definition of sin and what are some How does a person know when they are committing sin Anything that does not bring me closer to God is a If you think this is too strict just consider how ambiguous it This implies that staying the same is a A Christian should never be It does not imply that having fun is a It does not imply that sleeping is a It does imply that I sin every A perhaps simpler definition Anything that is counter to the two Great Commandments love God love your neighbor is a Anything I do that is not from love is a The same action can be a sin sometimes and not a sin I could yell at my kids as discipline all the time loving them considering only to teach them proper behavior or I could yell at my kids out of anger or I could post an excellent article because I am interested in sharing my opinions and getting feedback and learning or I could post an article because I want everyone to realize how wise I Chris Mussack